<%= react_component("TypedRailsActionExample", prerender: false, trace: true, id: "TypedRailsActionExample-react-component-0") %>

<h2>Typed Rails action round trip</h2>
<p>
  This form uses <code>createRailsAction</code>
  (<code>react-on-rails/railsAction</code>) with generated Rails response types
  from <code>react_on_rails:generate_response_types</code>. It posts JSON to
  <code>ContactMessagesController#create</code> and maps validation errors from
  the typed 422 response contract.
</p>
